{"tid":2363734,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"［生意額最低一日100蚊］本土服裝，老闆人手製作，即叫即做","createTime":"2021-01-12T12:06:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-16T21:15:45.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"ae1e7fb978a6401c041a7db9607b57cac0b5c1b3","tid":2363734,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T12:06:29.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">呢間黃店點樣告急法？一日賺100</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好屌鳩人用中銀就唔係黃唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ocx2G4k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOcx2G4k.png&h=5c4d7d6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人地好比心機做時裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />相信只係宣傳唔夠<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cWx96sW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcWx96sW.png&h=2e27523e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"gold\">唔講咁多，去圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n唔買都埋嚟睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有帽<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B67OBH6hbCZ/?igshid=1wti6khmaepwp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB67OBH6hbCZ%2F%3Figshid%3D1wti6khmaepwp&d=REZNLD6XKc%2F2J9Njm9EJuf3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=5b48b7a1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB67OBH6hbCZ%2F%3Figshid%3D1wti6khmaepwp&h=34db9e4a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B67OBH6hbCZ/?igshid=1wti6khmaepwp</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n有衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CIY1TTZFTS