tps://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCHv6NZYlfBM%2F%3Figshid%3D10a1wgvi25e6q&h=10bb5905\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CHv6NZYlfBM/?igshid=10a1wgvi25e6q</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n［生意額最低一日100蚊］本土服裝，老闆人手製作，即叫即做<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2363671\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2363671</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e9134148af4e6d062e702513e998cf84a1c00f9c","tid":2363734,"uid":89968,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T12:10:32.000Z","msg":"做生意唔一定會賺錢"},{"pid":"c4b4d065ed24b974ec8322f020ea9327f904f410","tid":2363734,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T12:12:59.000Z","msg":"想知間嘢開咗幾耐?"},{"pid":"4582e520f6389a5b12ff5ea308a80411a83b446f","tid":2363734,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T12:13:10.000Z","msg":"<ins></ins>"},{"pid":"b0e52e4dba1a4462be48709a422a097420467d13","tid":2363734,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T12:13:21.000Z","msg":"<ins></ins>"},{"pid":"a77266e5ed14783d6fb876d50db5c686342b6750","tid":2363734,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T12:13:31.000Z","msg":"<ins></ins>"},{"pid":"433e1b0566c1f81b4246dc29ac27b0819ad678bb","tid":2363734,"uid":12034,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T12:22:26.000Z","msg":"你不如貼件見得人既上黎睇下啦<br />\n<br />\n禁入ig頭幾件都係壽衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b13c4db3acc59891551c80300395fd3bd1d848a0","tid":2363734,"uid":347944,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T13:39:55.000Z","msg":"冇嘅，好野自然有人幫襯"},{"pid":"b0a73ffc8d61e690cdd9be2393ee30234607d837","tid":2363734,"uid":296890,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T13:46:33.000Z","msg":"唔好拎住本土個名賣啲冇質素嘅design啦<br />\n啲print搞到班tee level咁點叫人買<br />\n<br />\n仲有啲人唔好郁啲就整logo tee賣<br />\n你以為自己係名牌咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人哋用咁多年去build brand value先夠膽死賣logo tee賣幾千蚊<br />\n你啱啱成立又冇嘢去support 你賣logo tee同大學派啲ocamp tee有咩分別"},{"pid":"c41b9f7df4c80e833d9126a8443b651381527d7e","tid":2363734,"uid":3744,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T14:00:14.000Z","msg":"Cutting唔得 Model唔得 價錢唔得 <br />\n叫人點捨得俾錢去買 唔係唔想支持你<br />\n但我付岀金錢 都希望換取到一樣自己滿意嘅產品<br />\n真心 不如一切從簡 簡簡單單整啲質素好嘅淨色Tee/ Hoodie就算"},{"pid":"7bebc205344ab867db05e8c086f5bfca9f65f48e","tid":2363734,"uid":330227,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"c41b9f7df4c80e833d9126a8443b651381527d7e","tid":2363734,"uid":3744,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T14:00:14.000Z","msg":"Cutting唔得 Model唔得 價錢唔得 <br />\n叫人點捨得俾錢去買 唔係唔想支持你<br />\n但我付岀金錢 都希望換取到一樣自己滿意嘅產品<br />\n真心 不如一切從簡 簡簡單單整啲質素好嘅淨色Tee/ Hoodie就算"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T16:57:58.000Z","msg":"認真咩 <br />\nCutting 可能唔係個個啱<br />\n但睇返價錢我覺得幾百買件牛仔外套幾合理喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2ab7057e1f0ff87d51de3d4a81985e5a4b9b28c","tid":2363734,"uid":84415,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T17:01:04.000Z","msg":"nature selection"},{"pid":"101f3807ad8caf5177f34561b581bc77d5e793e5","tid":2363734,"uid":202872,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T19:15:38.000Z","msg":"有follow開呢間<br />\n佢訂一件要等4-6星期真心耐<br />\n而家買完著唔耐就春天<br />\n建議開始design夏季衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有個問題就係佢設計有抗爭成份<br />\n始終好多人會驚出街著件衫俾狗搞<br />\n可能要設計番一兩件冇抗爭成份<br />\n咁樣應該會多啲客<br />\n當然都要視乎designer意願啦<br />\n<br />\n雖然老細未必睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"987b6dacff72438c6d98a72de781af0ec8d96617","tid":2363734,"uid":18430,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T22:43:08.000Z","msg":"做生意包賺咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算好境搞生意，都大把人幾年無假放無糧出喇 <br />\n講埋條數出黎話18萬靠告急追剩5萬，已經好過大把人喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />開業得一年就想正數賺錢？咁做生意咪人人發達<br />\n仲要暗示自己無生意係因為信錯香港人，估唔到無人撐，依下難睇咗少少既，依家咩時勢，有閒錢多都買名牌先喇，無必要將個波拋返比香港人"},{"pid":"f53c568954645dae950b9f5c1fe26a177b4c5819","tid":2363734,"uid":66173,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T23:28:11.000Z","msg":"「畢業後可以直接去各大品牌擔任時裝設計師」<br />\n你連判斷自己有冇料都成問題<br />\n<br />\n先唔講cutting 物料 你啲graphics都係soc tee level<br />\n真心建議你摺埋佢止蝕離場<br />\n讀多啲書再睇下自己係咪有料做時裝<br />\n<br />\n唔好夾硬開post幫佢宣傳喇<br />\n情緒動員長遠唔係幫緊佢"},{"pid":"fb3c0c091bb8df78d9477846e63678842cfb59f8","tid":2363734,"uid":295079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T00:27:21.000Z","msg":"淘寶feel"},{"pid":"c5df6f7ff9f838c06a11df823bfe1c7dc2e103c3","tid":2363734,"uid":141782,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T02:53:24.000Z","msg":"佢d衫真係好撚柒吖嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b8140585947de3a37afe4152305f2760a751ef3","tid":2363734,"uid":141782,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"f53c568954645dae950b9f5c1fe26a177b4c5819","tid":2363734,"uid":66173,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T23:28:11.000Z","msg":"「畢業後可以直接去各大品牌擔任時裝設計師」<br />\n你連判斷自己有冇料都成問題<br />\n<br />\n先唔講cutting 物料 你啲graphics都係soc tee level<br />\n真心建議你摺埋佢止蝕離場<br />\n讀多啲書再睇下自己係咪有料做時裝<br />\n<br />\n唔好夾硬開post幫佢宣傳喇<br />\n情緒動員長遠唔係幫緊佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T02:55:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇完佢d衫<br />\n真係想叫佢不如返去讀書吧啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7be79532c65253e276fbe7891d860c6c49906028","tid":2363734,"uid":292564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T15:26:20.000Z","msg":"啲衫唔得咪無人買囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係好肉酸喎"},{"pid":"2fec7ce6d02e782914b91c9e7ebd1c0e8de823e7","tid":2363734,"uid":221468,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T15:34:39.000Z","msg":"真心嘅<br />\nprint tee就係睇graphic 但好明顯有待改善<br />\n就算係學生project都唔止係咁<br />\n出去儲多啲經驗再番黎啦"},{"pid":"ab3cfcf616f6df15993803e59e19aff62a109d71","tid":2363734,"uid":67447,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T18:04:14.000Z","msg":"可唔可以唔好冇人賣就賴香港人唔識貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n欠撚左你架咩"},{"pid":"d9bc64e15d4ba84ec7304b8b62b35b0e2cb09319","tid":2363734,"uid":376395,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T00:37:14.000Z","msg":"又開po?<br />\n<br />\n其實咁多次告急反映咗啲問題<br />\n<br />\n梁老闆你真係要反省一下自己盤生意啲出品同定價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n作為同路人 見到黃店告急當然會考慮優先幫襯<br />\n<br />\n但係唔會因為係黃而buy你啲design<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有阿老闆成日po story大大聲屌人黃店冇人買<br />\n<br />\n發哂悔氣成隻熱狗屌同路人咁 <br />\n<br />\n不如碌大隻眼檢視一下自己先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n難聽啲講 依家頂到你要識感激啦<br />\n<br />\n真係光復到你都好快乞米<br />\n<br />\n要同路人倒貼你盤on9生意其實似搵笨柒多啲<br />\n<br />\n利申：識老闆真人 對事不對人 不過你份人都好自大同有問題"},{"pid":"f1ab5101565de066173c3f49204572ce5d034484","tid":2363734,"uid":140198,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T02:31:50.000Z","msg":"書讀到一半就急於求成（唔好同我講輟學班富豪，呢啲例子係萬中無一）立志要自立門牌賺大錢，又吹噓到自己本身應該有條件做到大牌fashion designer，結果都係做graphic desiger搵食，大家都明斤兩去到邊<br />\n<br />\nCV唔係靠吹噓，係靠實幹的，忠言逆耳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3834aaff2f657056a9c5dd3ecd2749c15a2c642","tid":2363734,"uid":389648,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T03:53:50.000Z","msg":"「畢業後可以直接去各大品牌擔任時裝設計師」<br />\n哇咁依家真係委屈哂你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要返黎幫唔識貨既香港人整衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一係同大J合作囉,包你賺到笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee01984a62204d21abe706096a4b549999a66cc3","tid":2363734,"uid":157521,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T05:02:05.000Z","msg":"大佬最低限度你燙一燙啲衫先影沙龍啦"}]}